These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: pakistani, indonesian, nigerian
1. the nigerian is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the nigerian is between the pakistani and the indonesian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | pakistani | nigerian | indonesian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: satire, family, mystery
1. the person watching satire movies is between the person watching family movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
2. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | satire | family |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: reggae, trance, punk
1. the fan of trance is between the fan of reggae and the fan of punk##2
2. the fan of trance is on the left of the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | punk | trance | reggae |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: lizard, chinchilla, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
2. the owner of the pony is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the lizard##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | lizard | pony | chinchilla |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, mirinda
1. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking mirinda and the person drinking lemonade##2
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | lemonade | tea | mirinda |

 #################################

 
